  <heading>B</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Branch</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction branches unconditionally to a label at a PC-relative offset. This instruction provides a hint that this is not a subroutine call or return.</para>
    </authored>
  </desc>
